Learning Approach: Designed around active problem-solving, teamwork, and real-time feedback, this initiative gave students the tools to think like developers and build like professionals.'),
((SELECT id FROM programs WHERE slug = 'pes'), 'impact', 'Key Outcomes & Impact', 'Trained 100+ students through immersive bootcamp sessions combining technical depth and collaborative learning. 70% of students built fully functional web applications from scratch. 90% actively participated in hands-on coding exercises and real-time problem-solving. 100% expressed confidence in building, securing, and deploying full-stack web applications. 85% reported improved critical thinking and collaboration skills applicable across technical and non-technical settings. 92% experienced growth in communication and teamwork through pair programming and group challenges. 88% said they could now clearly articulate technical ideas, preparing them for interviews and presentations.'),
((SELECT id FROM programs WHERE slug = 'pes'), 'strategic_alignment', 'Strategic Alignment with PES College Goals', 'This initiative reinforced PES Engineering College''s commitment to: Skill-Based, Industry-Ready Learning. NAAC and NIRF Enhancement through Outcome-Focused Programs. Innovation and Startup Culture among Students. Improved Placement Readiness with Practical Tech Exposure. NEP 2020 Alignment through experiential, future-focused education.'),
((SELECT id FROM programs WHERE slug = 'pes'), 'conclusion', 'Turning Coders into Creators', 'At PES Engineering College, Rareminds didn''t just teach programming — we built a culture of innovation, confidence, and readiness. By empowering students to develop real solutions, communicate effectively, and collaborate as tech professionals, we helped transform the campus into a launchpad for tomorrow''s digital leaders.');

